  m_text: 'Now, let''s implement a simple health bar! We will keep using our Canvas
    object and adding new elements to it.


    In the Canvas, create a UI > Image
    object and call it HealthBar. Set its color to white. Now manually resize it
    to a thin rectangle, and move it to the top right region of the Canvas. Now,
    inside HealthBar, create another Image called Health with the same size, set
    its color to a shade of red, and its X pivot to 0. From the Rect Transform component,
    edit the Anchor preset to Middle Left.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
