  m_text: "EXERCISE 1: Implement MenuInteraction so that, whenever the \"Esc\" button
    is pressed, the game is paused/unpaused depending on the current state. \n\nThe
    game can be paused by setting Time.timeScale to 0, whereas in the \"regular\"
    unpaused state it is 1. This prevents the Update method of scripts from running
    and disables other core components of the Unity engine."
