  m_text: 'EXERCISE 6: Remember colliders? Time to use them again. Implement a script
    EnvironmentalHazard for the Sawblade on the floor (Hierarchy: Dungeon > Room3
    > Props > Traphome_Mid > Sawblade) which, when the Player collides with the saw,
    reduces the Player''s health by a user-specified amount.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
