  m_text: "In this scene, we'll discuss text and UI in Unity. \n\nWe will start with
    some UI basics first, designing a game menu with pausing and a working character
    health bar. \n\nThen, we will use a pre-generated text asset to scatter pieces
    of a story around the dungeon, which the player will then need to collect."
