  m_text: 'Let''s begin with the UI. Under the usual Canvas object, create a Text
    - TextMeshPro object. Resize it and move it to fit the left part of the Canvas,
    then remove the placeholder text. Disable the new Text object and modify our
    MenuInteraction script so that the Text is only showed when the game is paused.


    We
    will fill this Text box with the story chapters as the player interacts with
    books in the scene.'
